{"TopicId":139963,"ForumId":55,"TopicTitle":"Sugesstion: twin/Tri/quattro adapter betwin Small and tiny","CreatedByName":"Sereneti","CreatedById":163637,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-17T12:52:33Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Sereneti","CreatedById":163637,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-17T12:52:33Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nhy\u003Cbr\u003E\nthere are the 3 adapter from medium to small\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022190px-TVR-300L_Stack_Tri-Adapter.png\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 src=\u0022http://wiki.kerbalspaceprogram.com/images/thumb/7/73/TVR-300L_Stack_Tri-Adapter.png/190px-TVR-300L_Stack_Tri-Adapter.png\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nmy sugesstion is, the same adapter for small -\u0026gt; Tiny...\u003Cbr\u003E\nto attach some tiny engines on a small fuel tanks...\u003Cbr\u003E\n(like 4* ion on a small probe...)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-17T13:00:42Z\u0022 title=\u002205/17/2016 01:00  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 17, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Sereneti\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-17T18:40:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m going to re-make my age old request for stock Tweakscale on structural parts here.\u00A0 Pretty much every structural part in the game\u00A0 needs smaller and larger variants, rather than adding all of them, they could just add a very limited TweakScale implementation to structural (and modular wing) parts only.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThen people can use it to mod it on where ever they want with just a MM patch.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-17T18:46:52Z\u0022 title=\u002205/17/2016 06:46  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 17, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Alshain\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-17T18:58:23Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMight be simpler to make all rocket engines surface attachable like the Aerospike and Vector. Wouldn\u0027t really need adapters at all then.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the meantime, the small nosecone is your friend for making small engine clusters. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Sereneti","CreatedById":163637,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-17T19:06:43Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222587279\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139963\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463511503\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u002212858\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Red Iron Crown\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n6 minutes ago, Red Iron Crown said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nMight be simpler to make all rocket engines surface attachable like the Aerospike and Vector. Wouldn\u0027t really need adapters at all then.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIn the meantime, the small nosecone is your friend for making small engine clusters. \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:)\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_smiley.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:)\u0022\u003E\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\na rocket use the fuel in the \u0022line\u0022, not like a air breathing engine \u003Cimg alt=\u0022:(\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_sad.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:(\u0022\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\u003Cbr\u003E\nmaybe i would make a mod, with my sugestion, (if its simple, and someone cann tell me the basics)\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-17T19:09:55Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAttach a nosecone radially to a fuel tank and then put the engine under it, it will draw fuel from the fuel tank.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Alshain","CreatedById":110959,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-17T20:37:15Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYou can also use a cubic octagonal strut.\u00A0 Do the nose cones have two nodes, how would you put the engine under it?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ciframe class=\u0022imgur-album\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 height=\u0022550\u0022 src=\u0022//imgur.com/a/Rsoj9/embed?background=ffffff\u0026amp;text=1a1a1a\u0026amp;link=4e76c9\u0022 width=\u0022100%\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222016-05-17T20:38:44Z\u0022 title=\u002205/17/2016 08:38  PM\u0022 data-short=\u00228 yr\u0022\u003EMay 17, 2016\u003C/time\u003E by Alshain\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Red Iron Crown","CreatedById":12858,"CreatedDateTime":"2016-05-17T21:52:20Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00222587484\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022139963\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221463517435\u0022 data-ipsquote-useri